Recursive method for conversion of 'id-value' pairs to
a dictionary suitable for CBOR packet. Can be used for the nested
'id-value' pairs
Example 1:
 - Input: {
            'param1': {'id': 1, 'value': 55},
            'param2': {'id': 2, 'value': 77}
          }
 - Output - {1: 55, 2: 77}
Example 2:
 - Input: {'param1': {
            'id': 11, 'value': {
              'param2': {
                'id': 22, 'value': 2
              },
              'param3': {
                'id': 33, 'value': {
                  'param4': {
                    'id': 44, 'value': 4
                  },
                  'param5': {
                    'id': 55, 'value': 5
                  }
                }
              }
            }
         }}
 - Output - {11: {22: 2, 33: {44: 4, 55: 5}}}
